            <section id="data-use" class="legal-section">
                <h2><span class="section-number">3</span>How We Use Your Data</h2>
                <p>We use the information we collect for the following purposes:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Provide, maintain, and improve the CatchSpend service</li>
                    <li>Process receipt images using OCR and AI technology to extract expense details</li>
                    <li>Generate personalized spending insights and analytics</li>
                    <li>Send you important notifications about your account and subscriptions</li>
                    <li>Respond to your customer support requests</li>
                    <li>Detect and prevent fraud, abuse, or security issues</li>
                    <li>Comply with legal obligations</li>
                </ul>

                <div class="highlight-box info">
                    <p><strong>AI Processing:</strong> When you scan receipts, images are processed by our AI systems (powered by Google ML Kit and Gemini) to extract text. This processing happens securely, and we do not use your receipt data to train AI models.</p>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section id="data-storage" class="legal-section">
                <h2><span class="section-number">4</span>Data Storage & Location</h2>
                <p>
                    CatchSpend operates on a <strong>local-first</strong> architecture. This means your expense data is primarily stored on your device. Optional cloud sync features encrypt your data before transmission.
                </p>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Local Storage:</strong> All expense data is stored in encrypted local databases on your device</li>
                    <li><strong>Cloud Backup (Optional):</strong> If enabled, data is encrypted using AES-256 before upload</li>
                    <li><strong>Server Location:</strong> Cloud services are hosted on secure servers in the United States and European Union</li>
                </ul>
                <p>
                    We retain your data for as long as your account is active or as needed to provide you services. You can delete your data at any time through the app settings.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section id="cookies" class="legal-section">
                <h2><span class="section-number">5</span>Cookies & Tracking Technologies</h2>
                <p>
                    Our mobile application does not use cookies. However, our website and web services may use the following technologies:
                </p>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Essential Cookies:</strong> Required for basic website functionality and security</li>
                    <li><strong>Analytics Cookies:</strong> Help us understand how visitors interact with our website</li>
                    <li><strong>Preference Cookies:</strong> Remember your settings and preferences</li>
                </ul>
                <p>
                    You can control cookie preferences through your browser settings. Disabling certain cookies may affect website functionality.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section id="third-party" class="legal-section">
                <h2><span class="section-number">6</span>Third-Party Services</h2>
                <p>We work with trusted third-party service providers to deliver our services:</p>

                <h3>Analytics</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Google Analytics for Firebase:</strong> App usage analytics and crash reporting</li>
                    <li><strong>Crashlytics:</strong> Crash and error tracking to improve app stability</li>
                </ul>

                <h3>AI & Processing</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Google ML Kit:</strong> On-device text recognition for receipt scanning</li>
                    <li><strong>Google Gemini AI:</strong> Advanced receipt parsing and categorization</li>
                </ul>

                <div class="highlight-box warning">
                    <p><strong>Data Sharing:</strong> We do not sell your personal information. We only share data with third parties as necessary to provide our services, comply with law, or protect our rights.</p>
                </div>
